{"tid":509660,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"名宿韋亞感謝「父親」雲加","createTime":"2017-12-25T14:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T05:38:43.000Z","uid":333,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a0dc6b9cf0568ea2ca3a28610eaf5ca1ffb4c2ed","tid":509660,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:31:08.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=4wIt%2FDyNivndORFNwZq2V7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=0728d9c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】前世界足球先生韋亞視雲加為父親，並公開感謝該名阿仙奴領隊為他帶來非凡的足球成就。<br />\n<br />\n韋亞（George Weah）至今仍是唯一當選過世界足球先生的非洲球員，這名利比里亞中鋒曾在法甲球會摩納哥，跟現任阿仙奴領隊雲加（Arsene Wenger）共事，於其麾下度過4個成功的球季，之後效力巴黎聖日耳門、AC米蘭、車路士、曼城等著名球會。<br />\n<br />\n近期參選利比里比總統的韋亞說道：「他（雲加）是1位父親，把我像兒子一樣看待。當時種族問題仍然存在，他卻向我展示熱愛，希望我每天都在草地上為他效力。」51歲的韋亞又謂：「有一天練習得頗疲倦，我告訴他感到頭痛。他對我說：『佐治，我知道這十分艱苦，但你需要努力。我相信以你的天分，你會成為世界其中1位最出色的球員。』」<br />\n<br />\n韋亞補充：「我聽了他的話繼續下去，除了神外，若沒雲加，我也不會在歐洲球壇闖出一番事業。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"073e0824cf2a34b1b242d873d30c6bedd4e2918d","tid":509660,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:39:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c97c0a2669618f339cf58ede3ec82c9e239c5b2","tid":509660,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957850bf8daf95aa2f21e724e36a4a9a7652642d","tid":509660,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:42:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d571281d962054be42b0b5e511b194f51c4428b2","tid":509660,"uid":2949,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:45:36.000Z","msg":"雲加是神<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0384495a167bce746caad80b2d148452c17025cf","tid":509660,"uid":114483,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:48:29.000Z","msg":"唉，好心雲加好似費sir 咁早幾年就光榮引退，依家死纏爛打留係英超為咩呢，時代唔同左好耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb9c2a8026fd92f802ea444ebf0773d1bb2d492","tid":509660,"uid":77949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0384495a167bce746caad80b2d148452c17025cf","tid":509660,"uid":114483,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:48:29.000Z","msg":"唉，好心雲加好似費sir 咁早幾年就光榮引退，依家死纏爛打留係英超為咩呢，時代唔同左好耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:56:56.000Z","msg":"人地都話雲加是神, 神做既野又點到你D凡人批評"},{"pid":"2b82f0256196a54a6a632553a3a986befe1735d3","tid":509660,"uid":137644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0384495a167bce746caad80b2d148452c17025cf","tid":509660,"uid":114483,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:48:29.000Z","msg":"唉，好心雲加好似費sir 咁早幾年就光榮引退，依家死纏爛打留係英超為咩呢，時代唔同左好耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:58:42.000Z","msg":"佢拎多次英超就會學費sir光榮引退架啦"},{"pid":"2c714933e46337f9fecb7bd3fb8243706d11a338","tid":509660,"uid":333,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"2b82f0256196a54a6a632553a3a986befe1735d3","tid":509660,"uid":137644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0384495a167bce746caad80b2d148452c17025cf","tid":509660,"uid":114483,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:48:29.000Z","msg":"唉，好心雲加好似費sir 咁早幾年就光榮引退，依家死纏爛打留係英超為咩呢，時代唔同左好耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:58:42.000Z","msg":"佢拎多次英超就會學費sir光榮引退架啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:59:33.000Z","msg":"咁即係永續"},{"pid":"921049ea5a9c562b9dc75ad2b89fb7445f5d8c2a","tid":509660,"uid":8883,"like":1,"dislike":